Document: VisualShaderNodeTransformVecMult
Path: godot/classes/class_visualshadernodetransformvecmult.rst
Summary: A visual shader graph node that multiplies a Transform3D and a Vector3.

Inherits: VisualShaderNode < Resource < RefCounted < Object
Multiplies a Transform3D and a Vector3 within the visual shader graph. This node takes two inputs: a transformation matrix (Transform3D) and a vector (Vector3), and outputs the result of their multiplication operation. The operation is equivalent to applying the transformation matrix to the vector, which is commonly used for tasks like rotating or scaling vectors in 3D space within shader programs.
